Set of principles for delivering IT servers

Iterative and Incremental

1. Software deployment should be interative, frequent quick process- non-waterfall, agile
2. Should be continuous and automated
3. Responsibility
4. Avoid rolling out large sets of changes, espically big, breaking changes
5. Should not have long delay between development/deployment
6. Slow time to market - long bugfixes
